channel_map.snap_yaml:
name: convertermulti
version: 3.1.3
summary: Unit and currencies converter
description: A Unit and Currencies Converter. Converter Multi is immediate, fast and
  easy to use!
apps:
  convertermulti:
    command: bin/convertermulti
    plugs:
    - desktop
    - desktop-legacy
    - gsettings
    - opengl
    - wayland
    - x11
    - network
    slots:
    - dbus-convertermulti
    command-chain:
    - snap/command-chain/snapcraft-runner
    - snap/command-chain/desktop-launch
architectures:
- amd64
- i386
- arm64
assumes:
- command-chain
- snapd2.43
base: core18
confinement: strict
environment:
  SNAP_DESKTOP_RUNTIME: $SNAP/gnome-platform
grade: stable
layout:
  /usr/share/xml/iso-codes:
    bind: $SNAP/gnome-platform/usr/share/xml/iso-codes
  /usr/share/libdrm:
    bind: $SNAP/gnome-platform/usr/share/libdrm
plugs:
  gnome-3-28-1804:
    interface: content
    target: $SNAP/gnome-platform
    default-provider: gnome-3-28-1804
  gtk-3-themes:
    interface: content
    target: $SNAP/data-dir/themes
    default-provider: gtk-common-themes
  icon-themes:
    interface: content
    target: $SNAP/data-dir/icons
    default-provider: gtk-common-themes
  sound-themes:
    interface: content
    target: $SNAP/data-dir/sounds
    default-provider: gtk-common-themes
slots:
  dbus-convertermulti:
    interface: dbus
    bus: session
    name: com.ferrarid.convertermulti
